_______________________________________________________________________________
"Suggestion"       
        This is an annoyance power for psionicists to use for fun.  What
        it does is place a suggestion in the mind of the target for a
        couple of minutes depending on guild level.  The suggestion
        is a piece of text set by the psionicist.  Whenever the target
        types something OTHER than the suggested command, the target
        sees 'For some reason you feel like  doing <whatever> instead'.
        It does not prevent the original command from being performed,
        though.  It's just for fun.
 
SP Cost:  15		Guild Level:  1		Potential Points:  2
 
Command:  suggestion <target> <message/command>
